            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中石化(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1314:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1314\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1314-TW</a>)06日12:33上漲0.81元，股價漲停報8.92元，委買5張、委賣8,932張，成交109,469張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為石油化學產品CPL  AN  之製造及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中石化(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1314:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1314\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1314-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌2.41%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌4.92%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-20,403 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-19,454 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-949 張</li> <li>融資增減：+2,576 張</li> <li>融券增減：-261 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
